name: v3.7.0-cloud1
body:
* Tweak: Allow exiting to different WP screens [ED-6238] (#17637)
* Fix: Word spacing in Global Font Typography affects all texts on the site [ED-5749] (#18287)
* Fix: Missing esc translations (#17923)
* Fix: Favorites in Template Library doesn't work properly [ED-6528] (#18102)
* Tweak: Theme Builder - Open "Go Pro" link in new tab [ED-6396] (#18350)
* Fix: PHP 8.1 - Throws warnings in System info [ED-6869] (#18277)
* Tweak: Allowing manual insertion of negative values to numeric fields [ED-6909] (#18371)
* Tweak: Nested Elements - Infra [ED-6591] (#17957)
* Fix: Missing escaping translation to module onboarding (#18445) [ED-7022]
* Tweak: Custom size in image widget can no longer accept non-numeric characters [ED-7101] (#18570)
* Tweak: Added WooCommerce CSS variables (#18571)
* Fix: Container - Sometimes changing a control breaks the Editor [ED-7100] (#18569)
* Tweak: Controls - Added option to Number Scrubbing in numeric fields [ED-6910] (#18429)
* Fix: Shortcode doesn't work in popups or templates [ED-7126] (#18654)
* New: Notes - Promotion [ED-5523] (#18377)
* Fix: Images - Thumbnail files not deleted upon deleting its main image/attachment [ED-6973] (#18560)
* Tweak: Tag viewed Kit based on UTM [ED-7139] (#18688)
* Revert "Internal: DevTools - JS Deprecation Utility [ED-7003] (#18421)" (#18753)
* Add more thousands separators (#18026)
* Fix: Responsive state is not working correctly in Container (#18551) [ED-7314] (#18789)
* Tweak: Merged similar translation strings (i18n) [ED-7154] (#18618)
* Fix: Element is attached to the right instead of its original position when dragging it into a container [ED-7302] (#18802)
* Fix: Anchor Widget - Enforced better security policies [ED-7250] (#18806)
* Tweak: Added custom icons to various core widgets and features [OBXT-493] (#18231)
* Tweak: Added "em" unit for some widgets for border radius [ED-6775] (#17904)
* Fix: "Exit to" is not working after prompting the user to exit [ED-6927] (#18399)
* Fix: Overlay background is not visible [...] in Container (#18433, #18391) [ED-7315] (#18804)
* Tweak: Updated HTML A tag note in Container [ED-7368] (#18850)
* Fix: Columns control not pre-selected when choosing "Column" from the pre-designed container structures (#18390) [ED-7355]
* Tweak: Rearrange the Container panel for better discoverabilty [ED-7151] (#18788)
* Fix: Site Settings - Gradient background doesn't work in the Editor using global colors [ED-6994] (#18419)
* Tweak: Uploads Manager - Added filters to allow modifying upload temp paths (#18565) [ED-7410] (#18566)
* Fix: Control WYSIWYG - Enforced better security policies [ED-7249] (#18856)
* Fix: Improved CSS Loading - Style is broken after changing site URL [ED-7348] (#18922)
* Fix: Choose controls are not working as expected [ED-7373] (#18916)
* Fix: Container - Horizontal scroll is appearing when using direction Column [ED-7360] (fixes #18662) (#18966)
* Tweak: Added "Add New Container" right click option in Container [ED-7369] (#18967)
* Fix: Container - advanced padding is not working as expected [ED-7374] (Fixes #18314, #18414) (#18978)
* Fix: Global Colors - Gradient control doesn't work on frontend [ED-3517] (Fix #13288) (#18516)
* Tweak: Editor Loading - Try to increase memory in order to prevent stuck spinner [ED-7143] (#18962)
* Fix: Responsive - Can't change setting for a mobile background [ED-4305] (#18730)
* Fix: Fatal error while uploading & deleting files [ED-7394] (#19034)
* Fix: Elements - Eslint fix issue (#19063)
* Tweak: Modify experiments texts in Core 3.7.0 [ED-7591] (#19067)
* Fix: "Exit to" is not working when applying the same settings in the modal [ED-7583] (#19064)
* Fix: Alert Widget - Removed unnecessary CSS [ED-7596] (#19074)
* Fix: WIdget Common > Layout > Width not working responsively in 3.7.0 [ED-7641] (#19085)
* Fix: Media - Deleting an SVG file throws a fatal error [ED-7637] (#19087)
* Fix: Inner Section is not working in the Editor [ED-7579] (#19084)
* Fix: Can't drop image from desktop [ED-7646] (#19090)
* Tweak: Use user language in Elementor [ED-6556] (#18991)
* Tweak: Promoted some experiments to Stable and RC statuses (#19109)
* Fix: Typo in the onboarding (#19121)
* Tweak: Added default padding to containers [ED-7593] (#19132)
* Fix: Controls - Select2 gets a value of `null` when cleared in single value mode [ED-7698] (#19150)
* Revert "Fix: Select2 gets a value of `null` when cleared in single value mode [ED-7698]" (#19162)
* Tweak: Prevent dragging a parent container into a child container in Container widget [ED-7559] (#19141)
* Tweak: E-Icons - Added new icons for Notes and Loop features [ED-6779] (#19188)
* Tweak: Widgets overlapping issues on mobile when using containers [ED-7604] (#19153)
* Fix: Widgets disappear when the direction is set to a column in Container (#18880) [ED-7524] (#19144)
* Fix: Select2 gets a value of `null` when cleared in single value mode [ED-7698] (#19189)
* Fix: PHP Error when fetching System Info report for Experiments that don't have a title [ED-6879] (#19013)
* Tweak: Added EM unit to Elements Gap in Container widget [ED-7529] (#19197)
* Tweak: Kit Types section was removed from Kits Library sidebar [ED-7245] (#19209)
* Fix: User language is not being considered and not acting as expected [ED-7748] (#19207)
* Fix: License - Bad request [ED-7674] (#19212)
* Fix: Responsive Controls - Missing translations [ED-7782] (#19241)
* Fix: Pro license status is not being updated immediately after renewal [ED-7774] (#19247)
* Tweak: Add promotion for experiments (#19250)
* Fix: Fixed broken test - Added tag to test_add_feature (#19254)
* Tweak: Updated Container experiment description [ED-7675] (#19243)
* Fix: Research: Max-width for container [ED-7719] (#19258)
* Fix: Container -  RTL container arrow wrong side [ED-7456] (#19227)
* Fix: Timestamp in Onboarding data [ED-7140] (#18672)
* Fix: Editor - Typography control layout is broken [ED-7801] (#19260)
* Tweak: Added new Layout section to the Widgets panel [ED-7528] (#19264)
* Tweak: Updated content on Container widget [ED-7519] (#19265)
* Fix: Spacer widget is not working as expected [ED-7720] (#19261)
* Fix: Divider widget is not working as expected [ED-7722] #19224 (#19282)
* Fix: Align-self set to stretch is not working as expected in Container (#17052) [ED-7359] (#19281)
* Fix: Template library appears as empty when connected without pinged to template-connect [ED-5715] (#19246)
* Fix: WP CLI - Only 100 sites are processed on a multisite [ED-7834] (#18660)
* Tweak: Added 'em' border radius unit to general widget settings and global styles [ED-6775] (#18857)
